title: Fish diversity linked to Caribbean coral reef health

title_detail.value: Fish diversity linked to Caribbean coral reef health

summary: The health of coral reefs can be impacted as much by the diversity of fish that graze on them as by the amount of fish that do so, according to a new study. In the paper, the researchers untangle and unveil the powerful effects that biodiversity has on Caribbean coral reefs.
